                                </div>
                                <section class="pageStyles__SSection-sc-1navawn-4 ibLsRQ">
                                    <div class="pages__SBannerWrapper-sc-6zti4a-1 dXgqeu"><img src="static/banner-08401b4515705be60764f906ed1f3845.png" alt="WalletConnect"></div>
                                    <div class="pages__SDescriptionWrapper-sc-6zti4a-2 lbvZBb">
                                        <div class="pages__SColumn-sc-6zti4a-3 iHyPMU">
                                            <h2>What is WalletConnect?</h2>
                                            <p>WalletConnect is an open source protocol for connecting decentralised applications to mobile wallets with QR code scanning or deep linking. A user can interact securely with any Dapp from their mobile phone, making WalletConnect wallets a safer choice compared to desktop or browser extension wallets.</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="pages__SColumn-sc-6zti4a-3 iHyPMU">
                                            <h2>How does it work?</h2>
                                            <p>WalletConnect connects web applications to supported
                                                <!-- --> <a href="wallets.html">mobile wallets</a>. WalletConnect session is started by a scanning a QR code (desktop) or by clicking an application deep link (mobile).
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
